                    <!-- It is possible to translate the prose, by duplicating the elements head, desc or term, and adding xml:lang attribute -->
                    <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="en">Identify and verify format</head>
                    <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">Knowing the format of your data is the base for a decision on locating a conversion tool. If you do not know the format of your data either use tools to identify it or consult manuals that help you to indicate the format (e.g. in case of a file the file extension is a good hint to identify the file format). You should double-check your assumptions on a format, because some indicators can be misleading (e.g. a file can have a wrong file extension). Check if your conversion is feasible. Keep also in mind the output format, because some conversion may be not possible.</desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="en" type="terms">
